<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 13:12:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>盟友拒绝特朗普向霍尔木兹海峡派遣军舰的要求（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;德国周一断然拒绝了特朗普关于北约盟国派遣海军舰艇帮助保护这条战略水道航运的要求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;盟友拒绝特朗普向霍尔木兹海峡派遣军舰的要求（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 23:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>携带新旧干扰吊舱混合负载的 EA-18G 咆哮者正在执行伊朗任务</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;五角大楼的一份报告称，尽管新吊舱正在被用于活跃的冲突中，但它们仍然存在严重的初期问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes"&gt;携带新旧干扰吊舱混合负载的 EA-18G 咆哮者飞机正在执行伊朗任务，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 21:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>以色列声称摧毁“伊朗力量一号”</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/israel-claims-destruction-of-iran-force-one</link><description>&lt;p&gt;去年以色列空袭期间，伊朗政府的空客 A340 是伊朗国营飞机逃往阿曼的一部分。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/israel-claims-destruction-of-iran-force-one"&gt;以色列声称摧毁“伊朗一号”的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 16:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/israel-claims-destruction-of-iran-force-one</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国官员表示战争可能再持续三周（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/israeli-and-u-s-officials-indicate-war-could-go-on-for-another-three-weeks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;特朗普表示，他还没有准备好达成协议，而以色列则表示仍有数千个目标需要打击。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/israeli-and-u-s-officials-indicate-war-could-go-on-for-another-three-weeks"&gt;以色列和美国官员表示战争可能再持续三周（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 02:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/israeli-and-u-s-officials-indicate-war-could-go-on-for-another-three-weeks</guid></item><item><title>美国海军分配到中东的扫雷舰已转移到太平洋（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-assigned-to-middle-east-have-been-moved-to-pacific</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在中东承担扫雷任务的三艘濒海战斗舰中的两艘刚刚出现在马来西亚。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-assigned-to-middle-east-have-been-moved-to-pacific"&gt;分配到中东的美国海军扫雷舰已转移到太平洋（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 21:05:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-assigned-to-middle-east-have-been-moved-to-pacific</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-183</link><description>&lt;p&gt;应该买通用的！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-183"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 22:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-183</guid></item><item><title>无人机从海上袭击美国是已知的可能性</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/drone-attacks-on-u-s-from-the-sea-are-a-known-possibility</link><description>&lt;p&gt;联邦调查局关于武装无人机可能从船上发射的警报反映了真实的危险，即使眼前的威胁并不可信。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/drone-attacks-on-u-s-from-the-sea-are-a-known-possibility"&gt;无人机从海上袭击美国是一种已知的可能性，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 21:24:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/drone-attacks-on-u-s-from-the-sea-are-a-known-possibility</guid></item><item><title>部署到中东的海军陆战队远征部队：报告（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/marine-expeditionary-unit-deploying-to-the-middle-east-report</link><description>&lt;p&gt;搭载海军陆战队员及其车辆的海军舰队将为史诗狂怒行动带来一套非常灵活的能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/marine-expeditionary-unit-deploying-to-the-middle-east-report"&gt;海军陆战队远征部队部署到中东：报告（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 20:53:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/marine-expeditionary-unit-deploying-to-the-middle-east-report</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰公司被禁止出口Shahed拦截无人机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/ukrainian-companies-prohibited-from-exporting-shahed-interceptor-drones</link><description>&lt;p&gt;伊朗沙赫德无人机在中东地区发起的一波又一波袭击激起了人们对乌克兰拦截机的广泛兴趣。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/ukrainian-companies-prohibited-from-exporting-shahed-interceptor-drones"&gt;乌克兰公司禁止出口 Shahed 拦截无人机的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 18:56:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/ukrainian-companies-prohibited-from-exporting-shahed-interceptor-drones</guid></item><item><title>伊朗潜艇被 ATACMS 短程弹道导弹击沉</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/iranian-submarine-sunk-by-atacms-short-range-ballistic-missile</link><description>&lt;p&gt;ATACMS 和 PrSM 弹道导弹在远程摧毁伊朗海军方面发挥了关键作用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/iranian-submarine-sunk-by-atacms-short-range-ballistic-missile"&gt;被 ATACMS 短程弹道导弹击沉的伊朗潜艇&lt;/a&gt;后首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 17:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/iranian-submarine-sunk-by-atacms-short-range-ballistic-missile</guid></item></channel></rss>